Next, let's list all the bits a [[Markup_Parser_Stack]] frame's
[[mode]] can hold:

<< in [[Fabricator]] >>:
  PF_BOLD            = 0x01
  PF_END_BOLD        = 0x02
  PF_ITALIC          = 0x04
  PF_END_ITALIC      = 0x08
  PF_UNDERSCORE      = 0x10
  PF_END_UNDERSCORE  = 0x20
  PF_LINK            = 0x40
  PF_END_LINK        = 0x80

  PF_DEFAULTS = PF_BOLD | PF_ITALIC | PF_UNDERSCORE |
